31#include <engine/fifo.h>

33static void
34nvkm_gr_tile(struct nvkm_engine *engine, int region, struct nvkm_fb_tile *tile)
35{
36 struct nvkm_gr *gr = nvkm_gr(engine);
37 if (gr->func->tile)
38 gr->func->tile(gr, region, tile);
39}
40
41u64
42nvkm_gr_units(struct nvkm_gr *gr)
43{
44 if (gr->func->units)
45 return gr->func->units(gr);
46 return 0;
47}
48
49int
50nvkm_gr_tlb_flush(struct nvkm_gr *gr)
51{
52 if (gr->func->tlb_flush)
53 return gr->func->tlb_flush(gr);
54 return -ENODEV;
55}
56
57static int
58nvkm_gr_oclass_get(struct nvkm_oclass *oclass, int index)
59{
60 struct nvkm_gr *gr = nvkm_gr(oclass->engine);
61 int c = 0;
62
63 if (gr->func->object_get) {
64 int ret = gr->func->object_get(gr, index, &oclass->base);
65 if (oclass->base.oclass)
66 return index;
67 return ret;
68 }
69
70 while (gr->func->sclass[c].oclass) {
71 if (c++ == index) {
72 oclass->base = gr->func->sclass[index];
73 return index;
74 }
75 }
76
77 return c;
78}
79
80static int
81nvkm_gr_cclass_new(struct nvkm_fifo_chan *chan,
82 const struct nvkm_oclass *oclass,
83 struct nvkm_object **pobject)
84{
85 struct nvkm_gr *gr = nvkm_gr(oclass->engine);
86 if (gr->func->chan_new)
87 return gr->func->chan_new(gr, chan, oclass, pobject);
88 return 0;
89}
90
91static void
92nvkm_gr_intr(struct nvkm_engine *engine)
93{
94 struct nvkm_gr *gr = nvkm_gr(engine);
95 gr->func->intr(gr);
96}
97
98static int
99nvkm_gr_oneinit(struct nvkm_engine *engine)
100{
101 struct nvkm_gr *gr = nvkm_gr(engine);
102 if (gr->func->oneinit)
103 return gr->func->oneinit(gr);
104 return 0;
105}
106
107static int
108nvkm_gr_init(struct nvkm_engine *engine)
109{
110 struct nvkm_gr *gr = nvkm_gr(engine);
111 return gr->func->init(gr);
112}
113
114static void *
115nvkm_gr_dtor(struct nvkm_engine *engine)
116{
117 struct nvkm_gr *gr = nvkm_gr(engine);
118 if (gr->func->dtor)
119 return gr->func->dtor(gr);
120 return gr;
121}
122
123static const struct nvkm_engine_func
124nvkm_gr = {
125 .dtor = nvkm_gr_dtor,
126 .oneinit = nvkm_gr_oneinit,
127 .init = nvkm_gr_init,
128 .intr = nvkm_gr_intr,
129 .tile = nvkm_gr_tile,
130 .fifo.cclass = nvkm_gr_cclass_new,
131 .fifo.sclass = nvkm_gr_oclass_get,
132};
133
134int
135nvkm_gr_ctor(const struct nvkm_gr_func *func, struct nvkm_device *device,
136 int index, u32 pmc_enable, bool enable, struct nvkm_gr *gr)
137{
138 gr->func = func;
139 return nvkm_engine_ctor(&nvkm_gr, device, index, pmc_enable,
140 enable, &gr->engine);
141}
